column5: Feeling a little bit better wanting to go fishing tomorrow. Does anyone want to hook up and either go for crappies and perth at Keswick or Steelheading somewhere local.  Give me a call at work 416 651 6436 or post pm or call at home 416 531 4432 after 9:30pm.  Talk to you later,    Dave
Wow Dave, you must be definitely feeling better! I wish I could go tommorrow, but I've got too many meetings. Good luck where ever you end up going, and DON'T fall again!  Stan

Ahh, I would love to, but alas work is calling  , try me on a Wed/Thurs/Fri and ya just might get a different answer  But then with the way things have been going lately I'm not sure how much fishing will get done this year  , here's hoping.  Maureen
GOT SOME RIVER REPORTS FOR TODAY<  LOOKS perfect for tomorrow  Also tons of fish being caught in Keswick  Dave
Yes I'm going fishing tomorrow........in my dreams.  Good luck Dave.

I as well would love to go, if I knew where any of those places were... Spent today with my line in the water again and not one bite... it is getting terribly frustrating.  If you can not find a fishing partner for tomorrow Dave, drop me a pm.  Cheers,  Jen
